How Duchess Meghan and Prince Harry appear in the "Suits" finale
After nine seasons, the series "Suits" has now reached the grand finale in the USA. In the last episode there were many happy endings and just as many cameo appearances. And also the royal couple Prince Harry (35) and his Meghan (38), who worked for many years in the series, was paid tribute in a charming way. Warning, the following sections contain spoilers for the series finale.
First of all: Duchess Meghan did not return in the finale for a final farewell greeting as Rachel Zane, at least not for new scenes. Instead, some flashbacks once again showed the most memorable scenes with today's Duchess. For example, the moments of the failed and the successful wedding with Mike or how she greets him after serving his prison sentence.
